---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - OnPace Lease" description="Privacy Policy for OnPace Lease - your vehicle lease mileage tracking app.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <a href="/onpace" class="text-[#00D9A5] hover:text-[#00D9A5]/80 transition-colors text-sm">
          ‚Üê Back to OnPace Lease
        </a>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-12">Last Updated: January 20, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Overview</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            OnPace Lease ("the App") is a vehicle lease mileage tracking application developed by Erik Newby. This Privacy Policy explains how your information is collected, used, and protected.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-text-primary mb-2">Data You Provide</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">The App stores the following information that you enter:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-1 ml-2">
            <li>Vehicle name</li>
            <li>Lease start and end dates</li>
            <li>Annual mileage allowance</li>
            <li>Overage rate</li>
            <li>Odometer readings with optional notes</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-text-primary mt-6 mb-2">Data We Do NOT Collect</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-1 ml-2">
            <li>We do not collect personal identification information</li>
            <li>We do not collect location data</li>
            <li>We do not track your usage behavior</li>
            <li>We do not use analytics or tracking tools</li>
            <li>We do not collect device identifiers</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">How Your Data is Stored</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            All data is stored locally on your device using Apple's secure data storage technologies. If you enable iCloud sync, your data is also stored in your personal iCloud account, which is managed by Apple according to their privacy policies.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#00D9A5] font-medium">
            We never transmit your data to our servers because we don't have any servers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">In-App Purchases and Subscriptions</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OnPace Lease offers optional subscriptions and a lifetime purchase option. All payment processing is handled entirely by Apple through the App Store. We do not collect, store, or have access to your payment information, credit card details, or Apple ID.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            Your subscription status is verified through Apple's StoreKit framework. We store only whether you have an active subscription locally on your device to unlock premium features.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            We do not share, sell, rent, or trade your personal information with third parties. Your data stays on your device (and optionally in your personal iCloud account).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3">Your data is protected by:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-1 ml-2">
            <li>iOS device encryption</li>
            <li>App sandboxing (data is isolated from other apps)</li>
            <li>iCloud encryption (if sync is enabled)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            The App does not knowingly collect information from children under 13. The App is a general utility application not directed at children.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the App or on our website.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3">You can:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-1 ml-2">
            <li>Delete your data at any time by deleting the app</li>
            <li>Disable iCloud sync in Settings</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-2">
            <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:erik@eriknewby.com" class="text-[#00D9A5] hover:underline">erik@eriknewby.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <hr class="border-white/10 my-8" />

        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm italic">
          This privacy policy is effective as of January 20, 2026.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
